node.text: Introducing the RESISTOR LITE CHINO. Designed to feel weightless, this is the ultimate summer pant. Enhanced with super stretch and abrasion resistance, these pants can keep up with all your summer adventures. Experience the cool comfort of shorts with the sun protection of pants.

node.text:
🏔 BLACK BEAR PASS 🏔⠀
⠀
"When you think of going to the San Juan mountains this is the trail everyone thinks of and for good reason. It’s got everything; the views, the right amount of difficulty to get your heart racing and did I mention the views??! Okay so it’s definitely a new favorite trail to tackle and we hit the trail right at sunrise so we could take our time, enjoy the scenery and soak in the views without an audience or the pressure of others coming up. And nothing like starting your day with a view from 12,840’ with your best friends. Side note, the trail passes Bridal Veil Falls, the highest waterfall in Colorado."—@gary_babich

node.text: "I love this place. It’s kinda hard to get to and not very well known. There’s a popular spot close to it that most people go to not knowing this gem is close by. The views in the basin are second to none and the usually quiet and sparse population there make it ideal for me. I love the off the beaten path gems." Photo by: @nickwalk421// Location: Gold King Basin
